# {{ name }} (Python WASM Lib)

This is a minimal Python WASM library scaffold. It produces a reusable site overlay
that WASM apps can consume.

## Usage

Build via planner-selected derivation (requires exported Buck graph):

```bash
node build-tools/tools/buck/export-graph.ts
BUCK_TARGET=//libs/{{ name }}:{{ name }} nix build --impure -L --accept-flake-config '.#graph-generator-selected' --no-link
```

Inspect the overlay metadata:

```bash
OUT=$(BUCK_TARGET=//libs/{{ name }}:{{ name }} nix build --impure -L --accept-flake-config '.#graph-generator-selected' --print-out-paths)
cat "$OUT/BUILD-INFO.json"
```


